children.subject: We are still finalizing the panelists so we most likely will not be able to give advanced notice of who will be attending. As of right now, we have panelists who conduct research on multiphoton excitation in MRI and security/blockchain/quantum computing.
Hey, will we get advanced notice of who will be the panelists?

history.content:
Join our annual UC Berkeley IEEE Undergraduate-Graduate Research Panel on March 4th at 6PM PST! The Research Panel will consist of presentations on various research projects from graduate students at UC Berkeley, followed by an undergraduate-graduate student mixer. Learn more about what research is like at Berkeley, and find research opportunities under our graduate student panelists!

 

Please register at http://bit.ly/research-ieee to receive updates about the research panel!

Zoom link: http://bit.ly/research-zoom
